name: INTENSE ENGINE BUZZ! Air Canada A321-200 Takeoff from Calgary
description:
I'm a big fan of Air Canada's A320 family of aircraft, mainly because those CFM56s just sound so good on takeoff!

This A321 departure from Calgary to Vancouver was no exception, so I thought I'd post the longer version from the earlier trip report! (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5AHiE-KxPc)

Livery: New (2017)
Engines: 2x CFMI CFM56-5B3/P
Registration: C-GIUB
Route: Calgary (YYC) - Vancouver (YVR)
Callsign: AIR CANADA 203
Runway used: 35L (YYC) - 26R (YVR)
Date filmed: August 2021
